ank Stadium]]\n| align=center | 2017\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Chris Whalley]]\n|-\n| [[North Carolina FC U23]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.uslpdl.com/news_article/show/756005?referrer_id=2242498 | title=PDL Unveils North Carolina FC U23 as Expansion Franchise |publisher=PDL |date=February 10, 2017 | accessdate=February 10, 2017}}</ref>\n| [[Cary, North Carolina]]\n| [[WakeMed Soccer Park]]\n| align=center | 2017\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Dewan Bader]]\n|-\n| [[North Carolina Fusion U23]]\n| [[Greensboro, North Carolina]]\n| [[Macpherson Stadium, North Carolina|Macpherson Stadium]]\n| align=center | 1993\n| {{flagicon|NZL}} Tony Falvino\n|-\n| [[Tobacco Road FC]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.uslpdl.com/news_article/show/722378?referrer_id=2363587| title=Tobacco Road FC Revealed as PDL Expansion Franchise |publisher=PDL |date=November 16, 2016 | accessdate=November 16, 2016}}</ref>\n| [[Durham, North Carolina]]\n| [[Durham County Stadium]]\n| align=center | 2013\n| {{flagicon|USA}} Cedric Burke\n|-\t\n| [[Tri-Cities Otters]]\t\n| [[Johnson City, Tennessee]]\t\n| [[Kermit Tipton Stadium]]\t\n| align=center | 2016\t\n| {{flagicon|USA}} David Strickland\n|-\n| [[Virginia Beach United FC]]\n| [[Virginia Beach, Virginia]]\n| [[Virginia Beach Sportsplex]]\n| align=center | 2019\n| {{flagicon|USA}} Matt Ellinger\n|-\n| [[Wake FC]]\n| [[Holly Springs, North Carolina]]\n| Ting Park\n| align=center | 2001\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Gary Heale]]\n|-\n| [[West Virginia Alliance FC]]\n| [[Charleston, West Virginia]]\n| [[Schoenbaum Stadium]]\n| align=center | 2003\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} Daniel Smee\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:left; background:gray;\" | <span style=\"color:white;\">Southeast Division</span>\n|-\n| [[Daytona Rush SC]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uslleaguetwo.com/news_article/show/986002-daytona-sc-set-to-join-usl-league-two|title=Daytona SC Set To Join USL League Two|first=USL League Two|last=Staff|date=January 21, 2019|website=USL League Two|accessdate=Janua